states:

---------------------------------------
running
	activily serving  and can be redirected to

---------------------------------------
lockedRunning
	up and read, will not be selected for redirect


---------------------------------------
closingRunning
	graceful shutdown, 
	close when all users exited,
	will not be selected for redirect
---------------------------------------
booting
---------------------------------------
creating
	file system is being written

---------------------------------------
unloaded
	can be booted from this state
	will not be selected for redirect
	LIKE: just waiting for instruction